Output demos/create-card.gif

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 100ms
Set Shell "bash"

Hide
Type "export PATH=$PWD/target/release:$PATH" Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Type "# Create a new flashcard" Sleep 500ms Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "zen new What is the capital of France?" Sleep 500ms Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "Paris is the capital and most populous city of France." Sleep 200ms
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 2s
